snippet.title: NEW | SingStar™ Ultimate Party Launch Trailer | Exclusive to PlayStation
snippet.description:
No mics? No problem. Turn your smartphone into a pocket-sized mic and sing your favourite songs to entertain (or in some cases disturb) your mates. With the free SingStar™ app not only will your personal microphone be at hand for any harmonising emergencies, but you'll also be able to mix up your personal playlist and queue up the latest hits.

Everyone's got what it takes. SingStar™ Ultimate Party Out Now!

For all your latest SingStar™ news go to:
Website: http://bit.ly/1D6kkjU
Facebook: http://on.fb.me/1oxLH5z
Twitter: http://bit.ly/1uKBCi0
Instagram: http://bit.ly/1pEt0YF

Get your mic:
Visit the App Store - http://bit.ly/1wvXFxp
Visit Google Play - http://bit.ly/1sXqPmw
